  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00518', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'essay', '某研究欲瞭解：沒有吃早餐的學童，是否會比有吃早餐的學童在早上
