  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00519', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'essay', '某國家健康統計中心提出的報告指出，35 歲到 44歲男性的平均血液
